Grounded, now having fallen into a deep state of Stasis lock, was 
picked up by Terrataur.  Inside the bots mind raced images, once 
again of his ancient past and the everlasting battle between good 
and evil.  The face of good, his own, and the face of evil, the face 
that touched every last fear receptor in his cerebul circuts, much 
like his own.  This evil face, had once almost killed Grounded, and 
vise versa.   The images in his mind continued.  Of battles, and 
worst of all, the carbon life forms that were destroyed, by the 
recklessness of Grounded himself.
